sentences: Electronicos Fantasticos! was founded in February 2015 in Sumida, Tokyo by Ei Wada as a resident art project.
In November 23, he held his first concert called the First Ensemble Encounter.
In 2016, he participated in the Kenpoku Art Ibaraki Kita Art Festival with a team set up in Hitachi that tuned locally collected CRT TVs and electric fans into musical instruments.
